dominated strategy …

01:00:04.386 --> 01:00:06.210
or is it?
What's going on there?

01:00:06.210 --> 01:00:13.620
Why do you think 30% of people
are choosing Beta?

01:00:13.620 --> 01:00:17.920
Anybody?
Can we catch this guy here?

01:00:17.920 --> 01:00:21.503
Student: They might be
motivated by the fact that every

01:00:21.503 --> 01:00:24.500
