01:00:24.500 --> 01:00:26.809
Professor Ben Polak:
They could be moral people.

01:00:26.809 --> 01:00:30.080
So one possibility is:
this 30% of people in the real

01:00:30.080 --> 01:00:32.910
world who choose Beta are just
nice people.

01:00:32.910 --> 01:00:36.820
What else could it be?
Yeah?

01:00:36.820 --> 01:00:38.511
Student: I know this
might be changing the game a

01:00:38.511 --> 01:00:40.265
little bit, but if you ever
expected to play the same game

01:00:40.265 --> 01:00:41.526
with the partner you have more
[inaudible]

01:00:41.526 --> 01:00:42.880
Professor Ben Polak: All
right,

01:00:42.880 --> 01:00:45.789
they could be thinking they're
going to play again.

